data.value: Guidelines 1-Source files should be 1 column Header should contain "Serial Number"| "Instance number" | "Instance id" 2-Line details File sould be Unfiltered and have the header like the original downloaded file with the 6 extra lines and the Sheet should be calle "LineDetails" 3-when selecting Source Flles Path select the First one, keep in mind all files from that folde will be taken into consideration
